00:09:55.230 --> 00:09:57.230
simple editors.

00:09:57.230 --> 00:10:01.880
So for example, if you want to
create a JavaScript file, you

00:10:01.880 --> 00:10:06.200
can simply create this
file from the Google

00:10:06.200 --> 00:10:08.180
Drive Create menu.

00:10:08.180 --> 00:10:17.290
And then you can just write
JavaScript code in the same

00:10:17.290 --> 00:10:22.080
way that you can work
on Google Documents.

00:10:22.080 --> 00:10:29.750
So for example if you rename
the file from here it will

00:10:29.750 --> 00:10:32.820
update the file on Google
Drive instantly.

00:10:32.820 --> 00:10:39.120
And let me make this program
more sophisticated.

00:10:39.120 --> 00:10:45.320
So if you are working on these
files, you will find a lot of

00:10:45.320 --> 00:10:48.480
menu items that may look
familiar to you, because we

00:10:48.480 --> 00:10:53.040
