revisions just in the same way

00:11:03.140 --> 00:11:05.110
that you can do it
with Google Docs.

00:11:08.580 --> 00:11:12.770
So that was quite easy.

00:11:12.770 --> 00:11:16.440
So I thought, if that was easy
