00:11:30.630 --> 00:11:35.990
So if you open or if you see
these files in a folder you

00:11:35.990 --> 00:11:41.010
can just see at first sight if
that's an HTML file, CSS file

00:11:41.010 --> 00:11:43.250
or a JavaScript file.

00:11:43.250 --> 00:11:52.330
And you can also open multiple
files at once by selecting

00:11:52.330 --> 00:11:56.610
both of them and clicking
on Open With Editey.

00:11:56.610 --> 00:12:01.810
And this will give you
a simple view of both

00:12:01.810 --> 00:12:03.290
files side by side.

00:12:03.290 --> 00:12:07.130
So this makes working on
these files quite easy.

00:12:07.130 --> 00:12:10.810
And of course all changes will
automatically be saved on

00:12:10.810 --> 00:12:12.060
Google Drive.

00:12:15.685 --> 00:12:22.100
You can just resize the
different panels and you can

00:12:22.100 --> 00:12:24.860
open as many files as you
like in this view.

00:12:24.860 --> 00:12:27.330
So if you have multiple files
of the same type they will

00:12:27.330 --> 00:12:31.940
just be stacked in
the tap panel.

00:12:31.940 --> 00:12:37.180
And the nice thing is that on
Google Drive there's a secret

00:12:37.180 --> 00:12:40.680
feature, I would call it, that
allows you to publish files on

00:12:40.680 --> 00:12:42.700
the web as a website.

00:12:42.700 --> 00:12:46.560
So if you click on the folder
and select share public on the

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:52.300
web, then you can really
launch these files as a

00:12:52.300 --> 00:12:54.460
website on the web.

00:12:54.460 --> 00:12:59.560
And let me show you
how this works.

00:12:59.560 --> 00:13:02.230
So if you--

00:13:02.230 --> 00:13:03.290
maybe I was too fast.

00:13:03.290 --> 00:13:08.270
If you click on the folder and
say, Open With Editey, then it

00:13:08.270 --> 00:13:15.280
will open the website in the
preview mode, I would call it,

00:13:15.280 --> 00:13:16.700
or the website mode.

00:13:16.700 --> 00:13:19.500
So you have the different
source files on

00:13:19.500 --> 00:13:22.660
the left hand side.

00:13:22.660 --> 00:13:25.820
And you get a preview
of this website on

00:13:25.820 --> 00:13:27.310
the right hand side.

00:13:27.310 --> 00:13:33.540
So this is quite nice, to do
some kind of prototyping right

00:13:33.540 --> 00:13:34.370
on the web.

00:13:34.370 --> 00:13:39.410
Because you now can just launch
this website, post it

00:13:39.410 --> 00:13:42.440
on Google Drive on the web.

00:13:42.440 --> 00:13:45.270
And if you make any changes
to your source code, it's

00:13:45.270 --> 00:13:50.140
instantly visible
on Google Drive.

00:13:50.140 --> 00:13:52.640
But if you are working on a
real-world website you don't

00:13:52.640 --> 00:13:55.445
want to have this URL
starting with

00:13:55.445 --> 00:13:57.290
Google Drive or something.

00:13:57.290 --> 00:13:59.870
