00:23:12.340 --> 00:23:16.410
Editey, we started with the
very simple, basic stuff.

00:23:16.410 --> 00:23:18.890
And there's--

00:23:18.890 --> 00:23:26.080
at least in the midterm we are
planning to fill the missing

00:23:26.080 --> 00:23:28.870
features that you would find
on Google Docs, like

00:23:28.870 --> 00:23:33.700
commenting and [INAUDIBLE] and
real time collaboration.

00:23:33.700 --> 00:23:36.650
And so we are looking to
integrate that into Editey

00:23:36.650 --> 00:23:37.970
over the next weeks.

00:23:37.970 --> 00:23:41.140
So that's something that is a
little bit difficult for us

00:23:41.140 --> 00:23:44.670
