00:23:45.400 --> 00:23:48.400
And we have a bunch of
components that we can reuse

00:23:48.400 --> 00:23:49.290
in every application.

00:23:49.290 --> 00:23:54.670
So we may stick with it for a
while even though it's not the

00:23:54.670 --> 00:23:55.920
hottest stuff.

00:24:01.090 --> 00:24:03.120
As we are using Google Web
Toolkit, of course, we have to

00:24:03.120 --> 00:24:07.560
