wrapper for the real time API.

00:24:07.560 --> 00:24:08.870
So that takes some time.

00:24:08.870 --> 00:24:13.570
But once that is done, it's
quite easy to add features.

00:24:13.570 --> 00:24:16.150
STEVE BAZYL: I'd be curious to,
